    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips typical of regular use, while the interior remains comfortable and free of major stains or tears. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a responsive engine and smooth transmission that make it a pleasure to drive. It is a reliable choice for someone looking for a quality vehicle that has many miles left to give.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
